-- Petrobras in Talks to Buy Manguinhos Refinery, Folha Reports
-- B y   C a r l o s   C a m i n a d a
-- 2012-04-01T15:18:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/petrobras-in-talks-to-buy-manguinhos-refinery-folha-reports.html
Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4) , Brazil’s
state-run oil producer, is in talks to buy the  Refinaria de
Petroleos de Manguinhos SA  refinery in Rio de Janeiro for at
least 2 billion reais ($1.1 billion), Folha de S.Paulo reported,
without saying how it got the information.  Petrobras and Manguinhos declined to comment, according to
Folha.  Petrobras’s press office in Rio didn’t return a call and an
e-mail from Bloomberg News seeking comment. Officials at
Manguinhos couldn’t be reached.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carlos Caminada in  Sao Paulo  at 
 ccaminada1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Helder Marinho at 
 hmarinho@bloomberg.net  